libs.content:
find_library(turbojpeg_libraries
  names libturbojpeg.so.1 libturbojpeg.so.0 turbojpeg
  doc "found turbojpeg library path"
  paths
    "${depends_dir}/libjpeg_turbo"
    "${depends_dir}/libjpeg-turbo64"
    "/usr/local/opt/jpeg-turbo" 
    "/opt/local" 
    "c:/libjpeg-turbo64"
    "/opt/libjpeg-turbo"
    env turbojpeg_root
  path_suffixes
    lib
    lib64
)
